  "description": "The (3,5) pentagram torus: five crossings in the winding, pqScale=0.975, second only to the cinquefoil in coupling asymmetry. The five-crossing geometry creates a more complex interference structure than the three-crossing trefoil — more modes of resonance are active simultaneously. macroKnot=0.55 holds the matrix just past the Torus midpoint toward Solomon, keeping the five-star winding energy while introducing the two-ring paired architecture. Slow attack into a long sustain pad. LFO1 on filter at 0.04 Hz, LFO2 on braid depth at 0.07 Hz — two overlapping slow cycles that make the pad breathe without any discernible meter.",
